---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Self-referral services
intro: "You can refer yourself directly to many NHS and community services — no appointment with us needed first."
description: "Self-refer directly to NHS physiotherapy, mental health, sexual health, and other services in Fife without a GP referral."
breadcrumb:
  - label: Get Help
    url: /get-help/
  - label: Self-referral services
---

<div class="prose-content max-w-3xl mb-8">
  <p>Many NHS services in Fife allow you to refer yourself directly, without needing a GP appointment first. This is often faster and just as effective — and it frees up GP appointments for people who need them.</p>
</div>

{% set categories = [
  { "id": "physical", "label": "Physical health" },
  { "id": "mental",   "label": "Mental health and wellbeing" },
  { "id": "sexual",   "label": "Sexual and reproductive health" },
  { "id": "children", "label": "Children and families" },
  { "id": "travel",   "label": "Travel and vaccinations" },
  { "id": "other",    "label": "Other services" }
] %}

{% for cat in categories %}
  <section aria-labelledby="cat-{{ cat.id }}" class="mb-10">
    <h2 id="cat-{{ cat.id }}" class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-4 border-b border-gray-200 pb-2">{{ cat.label }}</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      {% for service in selfReferralServices %}
        {% if service.category == cat.id %}
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3 class="service-card__title text-base">{{ service.name }}</h3>
          <p class="service-card__desc">{{ service.description }}</p>
          {% if service.howToRefer %}
          <p class="text-sm mt-2"><strong>How to refer:</strong> {{ service.howToRefer }}</p>
          {% endif %}
          {% if service.link %}
          <a href="{{ service.link }}" class="text-brand-primary text-sm font-medium mt-2 inline-block" rel="noopener noreferrer">Find out more →</a>
          {% endif %}
          {% if service.phone %}
          <p class="text-sm mt-1"><a href="tel:{{ service.phone | replace(' ', '') }}" class="text-brand-primary font-medium">{{ service.phone }}</a></p>
          {% endif %}
          {% if service.secondPhone %}
          <p class="text-sm mt-1">{% if service.secondPhoneLabel %}<span class="text-neutral-mid">{{ service.secondPhoneLabel }}:</span> {% endif %}<a href="tel:{{ service.secondPhone | replace(' ', '') }}" class="text-brand-primary">{{ service.secondPhone }}</a></p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
{% endfor %}

<div class="mt-4 prose-content max-w-3xl">
  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">Can't find what you need? <a href="/contact/get-in-touch/">Contact us</a> and we'll help you find the right service.</p>
</div>
